comments: At the end of the drive, Nurkic (POR) and Siakam (TOR) come together and marginal contact occurs that does not affect Siakam's ability to make his intended pass.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact to start his roll to the basket.
Johnson (TOR) moves laterally into Lillard's (POR) path and the contact affects his SQBR.
Johnson (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by McCollum (POR) and any marginal body contact is initiated by McCollum.
Nurkic (POR) has a resting hand on Johnson's (TOR) back and marginal contact occurs that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
During the drive, Nurkic (POR) places a hand/arm to Johnson's (TOR) front and the contact affects his SQBR.
Nurkic (POR) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane at or about three seconds.
Boucher (TOR) makes contact with McCollum's (POR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by VanVleet (TOR) and cleanly blocks the shot.
VanVleet (TOR) draws Jones Jr. (POR) into the air towards him and the contact results in a foul on Jones Jr. (POR) even if contact is initiated by VanVleet (TOR).

During the rebound, Johnson (TOR) and Covington (POR) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal. Powell (TOR) secures the rebound and loses his balance before the ball is tied up and a held ball is correctly whistled.
Lillard (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Siakam (TOR) and has a resting hand on his back that he doesn't extend or deliver contact with.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Siakam (TOR) is out of bounds before releasing the ball is confirmed.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Powell (POR).
Johnson (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Powell's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Powell (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by VanVleet (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Powell (POR).
At the end of the drive, Jones Jr. (POR) moves laterally into VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs that does not affect his SQBR or ability to make his intended pass.

Jones Jr. (POR) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Siakam (TOR). Jones Jr.'s body only turns as a result of absorbing the contact initiated by Siakam as he jumps towards the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that VanVleet (TOR) is out of bounds is confirmed.
During the inbound, Lillard (POR) and VanVleet (TOR) engage and disengage off ball and the contact is marginal.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).

Johnson (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Powell's (POR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.  Powell tries to split the defenders as Anunoby (TOR) approaches and incidental contact occurs as they come together.
Covington (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Siakam (TOR) and cleanly deflects the inbounds pass away.
